{"tid":1249764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有冇法文撚]喺外國見到香港反送中上咗雜誌封面：Hong Kong is NOT China","createTime":"2019-06-21T21:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T06:05:12.000Z","uid":61170,"like":731,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"0f840ccbbccf2702739889d9cbfda50f9e3b744b","tid":1249764,"uid":61170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T21:00:32.000Z","msg":"呢幾日香港反送中局勢都好緊張，身處外國嘅我都從未間斷留意住香港最新消息<br />\n<br />\n今日食嘢竟然見到本雜誌係熟悉嘅畫面！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無奈本人唔識法文，有冇法文撚可以幫手睇下呢篇講緊乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/22/045314_833c84f88343ea5f10ed44d9efc0234d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F22%2F045314_833c84f88343ea5f10ed44d9efc0234d.png&h=58323698&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/22/045317_e8535a3e45058eb07306e626483a599e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F22%2F045317_e8535a3e45058eb07306e626483a599e.png&h=224bcae1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/22/045320_669ef492291267f7318b65233b6692dc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F22%2F045320_669ef492291267f7318b65233b6692dc.png&h=862d85fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/22/045322_eaca0d7b6aa9cc830f9af8dabae8dff7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F22%2F045322_eaca0d7b6aa9cc830f9af8dabae8dff7.png&h=991632c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/22/045324_355b1db81d8db2e2f6054426cab4340d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F22%2F045324_355b1db81d8db2e2f6054426cab4340d.png&h=c9c67908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔知佢講緊乜，但身處異地都見到媒體用4版咁長篇幅去報導，真係好感動！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港加油！<br />\n儘管仆街政府不瞅不睬，但係香港人嘅聲音係有用架！<br />\n傳到世界各地，比人知道我地香港咁細城市嘅力量！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">The world hears HongKong people sing!<br />\n</span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"73db770efc2439a8228d3cc401c4a6ced3cde9ab","tid":1249764,"uid":169232,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T21:01:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"210beddf653316239dbb2ca580b574f56a27028f","tid":1249764,"uid":22277,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T21:03:37.000Z","msg":"雖然唔知講乜但係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人並不孤單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d28459a55d6f37e6c5d7d04064bec82aed5624","tid":1249764,"uid":99324,"like":5,"dislike":75,"score":-70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T21:04:02.000Z","msg":"pish<br />\nbtw絲打隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8698f54a2748da9d372984a8465a2d077aa9e1db","tid":1249764,"uid":259675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T21:06:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"429da56a1e5f1e0cf875b6efd380aaa845cef2b4","tid":1249764,"uid":61499,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T21:10:18.000Z","msg":"Le monde 616之後有個漫畫係hong kong 拎住把遮係中國旗擋住紅雨"},{"pid":"7dc1fd71fdf2b7169e965e57743eb34f86cce8dc","tid":1249764,"uid":98431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T21:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be606118ec8e7eeef325f423a515d1b433e760d","tid":1249764,"uid":139027,"like":0,"dislike"