f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無奈本人唔識法文，有冇法文撚可以幫手睇下呢篇講緊乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/22/045314_833c84f88343ea5f10ed44d9efc0234d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F22%2F045314_833c84f88343ea5f10ed44d9efc0234d.png&h=58323698&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/22/045317_e8535a3e45058eb07306e626483a599e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F22%2F045317_e8535a3e45058eb07306e626483a599e.png&h=224bcae1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/22/045320_669ef492291267f7318b65233b6692dc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F22%2F045320_669ef492291267f7318b65233b6692dc.png&h=862d85fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/22/045322_eaca0d7b6aa9cc830f9af8dabae8dff7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F22%2F045322_eaca0d7b6aa9cc830f9af8dabae8dff7.png&h=991632c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/22/045324_355b1db81d8db2e2f6054426cab4340d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F22%2F045324_355b1db81d8db2e2f6054426cab4340d.png&h=c9c67908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔知佢講緊乜，但身處異地都見到媒體用4版咁長篇幅去報導，真係好感動！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港加油！<br />\n儘管仆街政府不瞅不睬，但係香港人嘅聲音係有用架！<br />\n傳到世界各地，比人知道我地香港咁細城市嘅力量！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">The world hears HongKong people sing!<br />\n</span><br />\n</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T23:03:20.000Z","msg":"睇完好感動...感受到香港人並不獨單<br />\n<br />\n有啲長同篇文有跳頁，我重點譯左第12頁開始嗰篇先。（盡力而為，不喜勿插）<br />\n<br />\n第12頁：<br />\n佢一開始已經讚揚我地香港人今次好團結所以先暫時阻到反送中，同時重炮係咁屌香港政府同建制派。<br />\n重點指出左反送中呢單野反映左一國兩制係幾失敗&mdash;&mdash; 行政長官唔係民選又高傲自大；建制以功能組別屈立法會人數，造成議會獨裁。導致管治系統專制獨裁(autocratic and totalitarian)，同市民嚴重脫節，漠視民意，根本係一個失敗(failure)同政制失效(the end of politics).<br />\n<br />\n第13頁(去到第二段飛左去第14版)：<br />\n呢啲嘅失效導致民眾有2014雨傘同69百萬人上街，但政府仍然不理，所以令人勇武，促成左612流血衝突。雖然唔知有冇成果，面對住暴力打壓，年青人走上前線，年長人後援，令我地取得階段勝利。呢次民眾更加超越左2014雨傘時勇武同和理非之間嘅內鬥同爭議，更團結去對抗。<br />\n<br />\n14版<br />\n呢次612成功係因為民眾無理成敗得失，亦無大台無人可以獨攬成果，令民眾眾志成城，去打呢一場為價值、理念同身分認(values, ideas, identity)同嘅仗。<br />\n<br />\n最後指出今次無內鬥係好緊要，所以比2014雨傘更成功。和理非有各界人士支持：學者、專業人士、宗教人士、社區人士等。而勇武亦以勇氣同決心，展示出直接、靈活、多變嘅抗爭手法。"},{"pid":"43ff09254be5ba24b4812de36fc41f1a63ca5684","tid":1249764,"uid":95499,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T23:11:39.000Z","msg":"其實成日都講<br />\n唔好拎香港係係世界焦點嚟打飛機<br />\n自己香港要自己救<br />\n人地鬼佬係當睇動物園咁嘅心態咋"},{"pid":"70bec14c704b5d686f2ac78d40d64b78d5da2813","tid":1249764,"uid":35364,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"38573b8b114c2f63f70b44a4001d4ffc59c558ef","tid":1249764,"uid":194243,"like":121,"dislike":1,"score":120,"quote":{"pid":"0f840ccbbccf2702739889d9cbfda50f9e3b744b","tid":1249764,"uid":61170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T21:00:32.000Z","msg":"呢幾日香港反送中局勢都好緊張，身處外國嘅我都從未間斷留意住香港最新消息<br />\n<br />\n今日食嘢竟然見到本雜誌係熟悉嘅畫面！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無奈本人唔識法文，有冇法文撚可以幫手睇下呢篇講緊乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/22/045314_833c84f88343ea5f10ed44d9efc0234d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F22%2F045314_833c84f88343ea5f10ed44d9efc0234d.png&h=58323698&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/22/045317_e8535a3e45058eb07306e626483a599e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F22%2F045317_e8535a3e45058eb07306e626483a599e.png&h=224bcae1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/22/045320_669ef492291267f7318b65233b6692dc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F22%2F045320_669ef492291267f7318b65233b6692dc.png&h=862d85fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/22/045322_eaca0d7b6aa9cc830f9af8dabae8dff7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F22%2F045322_eaca0d7b6aa9cc830f9af8dabae8dff7.png&h=991632c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/22/045324_355b1db81d8db2e2f6054426cab4340d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F22%2F045324_355b1db81d8db2e2f6054426cab4340d.png&h=c9c67908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔知佢講緊乜，但身處異地都見到媒體用4版咁長篇幅去報導，真係好感動！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港加油！<br />\n儘管仆街政府不瞅不睬，但係香港人嘅聲音係有用架！<br />\n傳到世界各地，比人知道我地香港咁細城市嘅力量！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">The world hears HongKong people sing!<br />\n</span><br />\n</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T23:03:20.000Z","msg":"睇完好感動...感受到香港人並不獨單<br />\n<br />\n有啲長同篇文有跳頁，我重點譯左第12頁開始嗰篇先。（盡力而為，不喜勿插）<br />\n<br />\n第12頁：<br />\n佢一開始已經讚揚我地香港人今次好團結所以先暫時阻到反送中，同時重炮係咁屌香港政府同建制派。<br />\n重點指出左反送中呢單野反映左一國兩制係幾失敗&mdash;&mdash; 行政長官唔係民選又高傲自大；建制以功能組別屈立法會人數，造成議會獨裁。導致管治系統專制獨裁(autocratic and totalitarian)，同市民嚴重脫節，漠視民意，根本係一個失敗(failure)同政制失效(the end of politics).<br />\n<br />\n第13頁(去到第二段飛左去第14版)：<br />\n呢啲嘅失效導致民眾有2014雨傘同69百萬人上街，但政府仍然不理，所以令人勇武，促成左612流血衝突。雖然唔知有冇成果，面對住暴力打壓，年青人走上前線，年長人後援，令我地取得階段勝利。呢次民眾更加超越左2014雨傘時勇武同和理非之間嘅內鬥同爭議，更團結去對抗。<br />\n<br />\n14版<br />\n呢次612成功係因為民眾無理成敗得失，亦無大台無人可以獨攬成果，令民眾眾志成城，去打呢一場為價值、理念同身分認(values, ideas, identity)同嘅仗。<br />\n<br />\n最後指出今次無內鬥係好緊要，所以比2014雨傘更成功。和理非有各界人士支持：學者、專業人士、宗教人士、社區人士等。而勇武亦以勇氣同決心，展示出直接、靈活、多變嘅抗爭手法。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T23:13:22.000Z","msg":"唔洗譯啦，第一篇係出自明報社論，<br />\n第二、三篇社論都係其他報紙譯返來<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ejinsight.com/20190617-beijing-can-do-without-a-hk-political-crisis-right-now/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ejinsight.com%2F20190617-beijing-can-do-without-a-hk-political-crisis-right-now%2F&d=ow9JOMNIA3MeF92spim0PrXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=eaedef1a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ejinsight.com/20190617-beijing-can-do-without-a-hk-political-crisis-right-now/</a><br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.straitstimes.com/opinion/why-hks-extradition-bill-damages-chinas-interests\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.straitstimes.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-hks-extradition-bill-damages-chinas-interests&d=ow9JOMNIA3MeF92spim0PrXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=d5cd1ece\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.straitstimes.com/opinion/why-hks-extradition-bill-damages-chinas-interests</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"b973227c7f3fc578604251ce56600330a3ea81b3","tid":1249764,"uid":52605,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"43ff09254be5ba24b4812de36fc41f1a63ca5684","tid":1249764,"uid":95499,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T23:11:39.000Z","msg":"其實成日都講<br />\n唔好拎香港係係世界焦點嚟打飛機<br />\n自己香港要自己救<br />\n人地鬼佬係當睇動物園咁嘅心態咋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T23:18:25.000Z","msg":"所以話有乜咁感動<br />\n你睇其他國家反暴政咪又係當新聞咁睇<br />\n唔好幻想歐美會救香港<br />\n香港人要靠自己"},{"pid":"ae67424996a68d262a44c5a37e530c00e8fc70f6","tid":1249764,"uid":35364,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"b973227c7f3fc578604251ce56600330a3ea81b3","tid":12